    %% Early Detection Path
    B -->|Early Detection| D[Detection Services]
    D -->|For Hospitals| D1[OpenCV Patient Monitoring]
    D1 --> D2[24/7 Movement Tracking]
    D2 --> D3[Unusual Movement Detection]
    D3 --> D4[Alert System]
    D -->|For Users| D5[Medical Report Scanner]
    D5 --> D6[AI Analysis]
